description:
## The Middle Element Problem

A module provisions IAM users from a list:

```hcl
variable "users" {
  default = ["alice", "bob", "carol"]
}

resource "aws_iam_user" "this" {
  count = length(var.users)
  name  = var.users[count.index]
}
```

You remove `"bob"` from the list. You run `terraform plan` and are alarmed to see that the **carol** user is scheduled to be destroyed and recreated, even though only bob was removed.

What is happening, and what is the correct fix?
